wiki.summary: “Taste”, a trap-influenced, upbeat rap song featuring Migos’ member Offset was published on May 16, 2018. The track marks T-Raww and Offset’s first ever collaboration. Tyga explained how the song came about: “I sent it to [Offset] and he FaceTimed me and told me the song was crazy and he wanted to hop on it.” A music video was released on the same day, depicting Tyga and Offset surrounded by girls dancing to the song at a house party by the pool and on a roller rink. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: “Taste”, a trap-influenced, upbeat rap song featuring Migos’ member Offset was published on May 16, 2018. The track marks T-Raww and Offset’s first ever collaboration. Tyga explained how the song came about: “I sent it to [Offset] and he FaceTimed me and told me the song was crazy and he wanted to hop on it.” A music video was released on the same day, depicting Tyga and Offset surrounded by girls dancing to the song at a house party by the pool and on a roller rink. Cameo appearances by A.E., Wiz Khalifa, Ronny J, Joyner Lucas, 2 Chainz and comedian King Bach are featured throughout the video. Read more on Last.fm.
